-tri-%C3%A2m/poem-QpvXdas2cMA4xjQDYutA3A">Tặng tri âm - 贈知音</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Qu%C3%A2n/author-VkIfi7DKP2f1cM8JZZP8yA">Ôn Đình Quân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BB%99ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-chi%E1%BA%BFn-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ca/poem-r-0sKzn4t1sF64MC4QGgRg">Thạch tướng quân chiến trường ca - 石將軍戰場歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BB%99ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-QwR8mfkWimm7tarlC84k4w">Lý Mộng Dương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/Thi%C3%AAn-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-v%C3%A3n-v%E1%BB%8Dng/poem-g4iiwlfx7vmjQbl_kcUYIg">Thiên Trường vãn vọng - 天長晚望</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-EY7jN0xHQfiiJpD91KwIgw">Trần Nhân Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Dao-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Thu-c%E1%BA%A7m/poem-QTlSjoIYxEH32y-lLwX0mQ">Thu cầm - 秋琴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Dao-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-6wSObbfs4FHPyd4s5oXZ7Q">Vương Dao Tương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-T%E1%BB%B1-Thanh/Thu-v%C3%A3n/poem-xw7w73rt-Z69DSvWAmiaIw">Thu vãn - 秋晚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-T%E1%BB%B1-Thanh/author-wQICzKRVau8PqmJ28C9K6g">Cao Tự Thanh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
